{
  "message": "fix: v2.7.11 - Make better-sqlite3 installation failures graceful for npx\n\n- Updated postinstall scripts to not fail on errors\n- Added .npmrc to handle optional dependency failures\n- Improved install-arm64.js error handling\n- Ensures claude-flow works in environments without build tools (Codespaces, Docker, etc.)\n- Falls back to in-memory storage when SQLite unavailable",
